                    <li>Check to make sure the name of the book you're trying to find isn't misspelled.</li>
                    <li>If the title you are trying to find is a valid title, the daily limit provided by Google Books may have been exceeded. Try again tomorrow.</li>
                  </ol>    
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingSeven">
